THE OCEAN WAVES

6
00:02:06,093 --> 00:02:10,723
“Thank you for your patience,
the plane is about to take off.”

7
00:02:19,706 --> 00:02:23,516
Yutaka and! first met Rikako
two years ago.

8
00:02:24,144 --> 00:02:27,684
it was the summer
of our junior year.

9
00:02:38,492 --> 00:02:41,772
Yutaka called me at work.

10
00:02:43,497 --> 00:02:46,217
Hurry up kid!
More dishes! Keep'em coming!

11
00:02:46,733 --> 00:02:47,813
OK!

12
00:02:48,802 --> 00:02:51,082
Taku, telephone!

13
00:02:51,505 --> 00:02:52,465
Coming.

14
00:02:55,509 --> 00:02:56,238
Hello.

15
00:02:56,443 --> 00:02:58,343
- Taku?
- Hey, Yutaka.

16
00:02:58,979 --> 00:03:01,699
Come to school
as soon as you finish today.

17
00:03:02,182 --> 00:03:05,112
i be here waiting for you.

18
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:06,829
OK.

19
00:03:07,988 --> 00:03:11,498
Sorry. have to leave
early today.

20
00:03:12,092 --> 00:03:13,432
Now wait a minute!

21
00:03:14,528 --> 00:03:16,078
See you tomorrow!

22
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,780
You can't rely on kids!

23
00:03:29,443 --> 00:03:30,553
See you!

24
00:04:06,313 --> 00:04:07,333
Yutaka!

25
00:04:07,681 --> 00:04:09,111
You got here fast.

26
00:04:09,416 --> 00:04:10,786
You told me to!

27
00:04:11,084 --> 00:04:11,954
Take a look.

28
00:04:16,923 --> 00:04:18,653
Who is it? l can’t see.

29
00:04:19,358 --> 00:04:21,969
Just transferred to my class.

30
00:04:22,429 --> 00:04:23,659
Her name's Rikako Muto.

31
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:25,660
- From next semester?
- Yeah.

32
00:04:26,166 --> 00:04:29,386
A mid-year transfer?
That's unusual.

33
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:32,546
She moved here
from Tokyo, that's why.

34
00:04:33,607 --> 00:04:36,647
[ just showed her
around the school.

35
00:04:37,177 --> 00:04:39,927
That's right,
you're on the student council.

36
00:04:40,547 --> 00:04:42,447
You really like her, huh?

37
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:46,459
Anyone would,
she's really good looking.

38
00:04:47,053 --> 00:04:47,813
Really?

39
00:04:51,191 --> 00:04:54,700
l can't tell, and we can't just
walk down and look.

40
00:04:55,529 --> 00:04:58,159
If you want,
we can go down...

41
00:04:58,632 --> 00:05:01,182
...and say we have a question.

42
00:05:01,635 --> 00:05:04,094
Nah, let's not
go that far.

43
00:05:05,138 --> 00:05:07,858
The teachers know
I'm working this summer...

44
00:05:08,341 --> 00:05:10,211
...and not taking classes.

45
00:05:11,077 --> 00:05:13,977
Still mad about
the jr. high school trip?

46
00:05:14,648 --> 00:05:17,988
I don't like the way
they just cancelled it...

47
00:05:18,552 --> 00:05:20,452
...and tried to buy us off
with Hawaii in high school.

48
00:05:20,821 --> 00:05:23,071
Do they think we're stupid?

49
00:05:23,957 --> 00:05:28,296
Everyone's excited.
l think it was a good move.

50
00:05:29,629 --> 00:05:33,549
A relaxing trip will help us
cram for college entrance exams.

51
00:05:36,937 --> 00:05:40,917
Hawaii's expensive.
I need to make some money.

52
00:05:42,576 --> 00:05:46,476
Just remember to keep up
with your studies.

53
00:05:47,113 --> 00:05:48,223
Don't fall behind.

54
00:05:48,481 --> 00:05:49,471
Sure. By the way...

55
00:05:49,816 --> 00:05:53,595
...was there something
you wanted to talk about?

56
00:05:54,187 --> 00:05:56,907
Not really.
I just felt like seeing you.

57
00:05:57,724 --> 00:05:59,974
I'll get my bike.
Wait by the gate.

58
00:06:07,367 --> 00:06:10,327
All through jr. high school
and high school...

59
00:06:11,037 --> 00:06:14,227
... Yutaka and!
were never in the same class.

60
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:19,762
Even so, ! always felt
he was a close friend.

61
00:06:21,615 --> 00:06:24,165
it all started in our last year
of jr. high school...

62
00:06:24,618 --> 00:06:28,397
...When the school trip to Kyoto was
suddenly cancelled.

63
00:06:29,022 --> 00:06:32,892
“We regret to announce
that this year's jr. high school trip...”

64
00:06:33,526 --> 00:06:34,756
“..bas been cancelled.”

65
00:06:35,028 --> 00:06:40,248
‘In future. jr. high and high school
trips will be combined.”

66
00:06:42,402 --> 00:06:43,982
“Last year, our college
placement results...”

67
00:06:44,304 --> 00:06:47,263
“... were lower than the
prefectural high school.”

68
00:06:48,375 --> 00:06:51,885
“Our school's proud traditions
and your obligations to your parents...”

69
00:06:52,479 --> 00:06:54,529
“..make this completely unacceptable. ”

70
00:06:55,448 --> 00:06:57,178
“To restore our school's honor...”

71
00:06:57,517 --> 00:07:01,587
“... the high school seniors
must redouble their efforts.”

72
00:07:02,255 --> 00:07:06,175
“You must set an example
for our jr. high school seniors. ”

73
00:07:07,861 --> 00:07:10,961
Let's go see Miss Sayama.
Come on, Taku!

74
00:07:14,668 --> 00:07:16,448
The whole thing was so stupid...

75
00:07:16,937 --> 00:07:19,627
...we decided to complain
to our home room teacher.

76
00:07:27,447 --> 00:07:30,197
We all think this is unfair.

77
00:07:30,917 --> 00:07:34,457
Canceling the trip
won't help our grades.

78
00:07:35,355 --> 00:07:38,865
The school owes us
a detailed explanation.

79
00:07:40,026 --> 00:07:43,046
Ask for one
when your grades are better!

80
00:07:45,031 --> 00:07:47,311
I'm already a top student!

81
00:07:50,236 --> 00:07:54,596
Don't pressure Miss Sayama
just because she's a woman!

82
00:07:57,944 --> 00:08:01,254
We thought that was the end
of the matter.

83
00:08:02,282 --> 00:08:05,301
But a week later,
at the morning assembly —

84
00:08:11,725 --> 00:08:16,415
Your parents have also approved
the trip cancellation.

85
00:08:17,163 --> 00:08:22,053
lf you're still not satisfied,
we'll explain the decision.

86
00:08:23,069 --> 00:08:26,729
Raise your hand
if you're still not satisfied.

87
00:08:36,482 --> 00:08:37,712
He's got guts.

88
00:08:39,085 --> 00:08:41,275
it was Yutaka Matsuno.

89
00:08:42,087 --> 00:08:43,257
OK.

90
00:08:43,523 --> 00:08:46,453
We'll explain the decision for students
who raised their hands.

91
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,980
Go to the art room
after classes. Dismissed!

